# Dashboard API Tests

### Get Student Dashboard (requires authentication)
GET https://localhost:7000/api/Dashboard/student
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Get Student Dashboard by ID (admin/teacher access)
GET https://localhost:7000/api/Dashboard/student/{{studentId}}
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Example with actual student ID (replace with real ID)
GET https://localhost:7000/api/Dashboard/student/12345678-1234-1234-1234-123456789012
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Test with a real token (replace YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE with actual token)
GET https://localhost:7000/api/Dashboard/student
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiIxMjM0NTY3OC0xMjM0LTEyMzQtMTIzNC0xMjM0NTY3ODkwMTIiLCJlbWFpbCI6InRlc3RAdGVzdC5jb20iLCJyb2xlIjoiU3R1ZGVudCIsIm5hbWUiOiJUZXN0IFVzZXIiLCJleHAiOjE3MDQwNzM2MDAsImlhdCI6MTcwNDA3MDAwMH0.example_signature

# Password Reset API Tests

### Request password reset for regular email (should send email to user)
POST https://localhost:7000/api/Auth/request-reset
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "student@example.com"
}

### Request password reset for @bga.al email (should notify supervisor)
POST https://localhost:7000/api/Auth/request-reset
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john.doe@bga.al"
}

### Reset password with token (works for both regular and @bga.al emails)
POST https://localhost:7000/api/Auth/reset
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "YOUR_RESET_TOKEN_HERE",
  "newPassword": "NewSecurePassword123!"
}

# Supervisor Dashboard Tests

### Get supervisor dashboard (should show pending password reset requests)
GET https://localhost:7000/api/Supervisor/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_SUPERVISOR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Get pending password reset requests for supervisor
GET https://localhost:7000/api/Supervisor/password-reset-requests
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_SUPERVISOR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE


### Handle password reset request (supervisor action - auto-generate one-time password)
POST https://localhost:7000/api/Supervisor/students/4ef3c745-c3ad-4941-8b9e-1c235e1c0b2c/password-reset
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_SUPERVISOR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

true

### Reject password reset request (supervisor action)
POST https://localhost:7000/api/Supervisor/students/4ef3c745-c3ad-4941-8b9e-1c235e1c0b2c/password-reset
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_SUPERVISOR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

false